20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20the%20water%20was%20significantly%20warmer%20than%20in%20Taormina%2C%20where%20we%20had%20been%20before.%20Days%20later%2C%20a%20guide%20explained%20that%20it%20was%20due%20to%20the%20volcano's%20hydrothermal%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22655a0862-66fe-45d8-8679-6c8e0f57a345%5C%22%3EWe%20took%20a%20boat%20to%20see%20the%20eruptions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20side%20of%20the%20island%2C%20you%20can%20find%20houses%2C%20restaurants%2C%20the%20port%2C%20and%20a%20church.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20you%20have%20the%20Sciara%20del%20Fuocco%2C%20where%20you%20can%20see%20the%20volcano%20erupt%20every%2015%20minutes%20or%20so%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20hiking%20companies%20offer%20tours%20to%20explore%20the%20volcano%2C%20taking%20you%20up%20to%20400%20meters%20from%20the%20erupting%20area.%20Because%20our%20kids%20are%20little%20and%20the%20hike%20is%20hours%20long%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20boat%20instead%20and%20watch%20the%20eruptions%20from%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stromboli%20volcano%20eruption%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68642be7f748d8c055f4bfc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20took%20a%20boat%20to%20see%20the%20Sciara%20del%20Fuoco.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20at%20dusk%20since%20it's%20better%20to%20see%20the%20lava%20when%20it's%20dark%20out.%20I%20figured%20we'd%20just%20see%20some%20splutter%20and%20smoke%2C%20but%20I%20was%20astonished%20as%20we%20watched%20full-on%20eruptions%20that%20trickled%20lava%20back%20into%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295244472-6286-4202-9ea7-f742f1179e51%5C%22%3EShips%20bring%20water%20to%20the%20island%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20first%20night%20at%20Stromboli%2C%20I%20