ure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOver%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20thought%20we'd%20built%20the%203%2C000-square-foot%20home%20of%20our%20dreams.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20added%20extra%20bathrooms%2C%20another%20bedroom%2C%20and%20focused%20on%20having%20tons%20of%20space%20for%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThings%20didn't%20go%20as%20planned.%20Now%2C%20our%20home%20feels%20too%20big%2C%20and%20we%20regret%20some%20of%20our%20choices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20millennials%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20long%20been%20aware%20that%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-homeowners-housing-shortage-falling-prices-values-baby-boomers-population-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elikelihood%20of%20home%20ownership%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20abysmal.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20the%202007%20subprime%20mortgage%20crisis%20was%20still%20fresh%20in%20our%20memories%20as%20we%20began%20designing%20our%20future.%20So%2C%20in%202009%2C%20when%20we%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20our%20own%20home%20built%2C%20we%20went%20all%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20we%20were%20sharing%20a%20bedroom%20in%20my%20parents%E2%80%99%20home%20with%20our%2015-month-old%2C%20and%20I'd%20just%20discovered%20I%20was%20pregnant%20again.%20Talks%20of%20getting%20a%20house%20happened%20quickly%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20more%20like%20wishful%20thinking%20than%20something%20that%20would%20pan%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20looked%20into%20it%2C%20we%20were%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20we%20qualified%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Ffha-loan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFHA%20loan%20to%20finance%20a%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20found%20that%20home%20builders%20were%20relatively%20desperate%20to%20sell%20homes%20in%20order%20to%20offload%20properties%20they%20were%20saddled%20with%20after%20the%20housing%20crisis.%20This%20meant%20that%20the%20builders%20and%20their%20lenders%20were%20very%20accommodating%20of%20us%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders-first-time-buyers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst-time%20home%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20were%20taking%20the%20plunge%20anyway%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20the%20house%20of%20our%20dreams%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20go%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228eadfab5-2214-481f-97e5-0fd71d1f9608%5C%22%3EWe%20had%20ideas%20for%20using%20a%20big%20house%2C%20but%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20work%20out%20as%20we%E2%80%99d%20planned%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22House%20structure%20being%20framed%20out%20of%20wood%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d94a73d5881a51c1c2a2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDesigning%20a%20house%20you'd%20like%20to%20stay%20in%20forever%20can%20be%20difficult.%3Cp%3EKirk%20Fisher%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20a%20roughly%203%2C000-square-foot%20layout%20for%20our%20home%20and%20prioritized%20having%20lots%20of%20rooms.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20home%20builder%20offered%20us%20a%20%2415%2C000%20upgrade%20credit%20that%20we%20used%20to%20add%20a%20powder%20room%20and%20an%20additional%20large%20bedroom%20with%20an%20ensuite%20bathroom%20similar%20to%20the%20primary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20additions%20put%20the%20home%20layout%20at%20five%20bedrooms%20and%20three-and-a-half%20baths.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20house%20plan%20included%20both%20formal%20and%20casual%20dining%20rooms%20and%20a%20private%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20have%20seemed%20like%20a%20lot%20for%20our%20small%20family%2C%20but%20we%20planned%20to%20use%20the%20space%20and%20fill%20it%20with%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20open%20to%20having%20more%20kids%20and%20planned%20to%20have%20my%20parents%20move%20in%20with%20us%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-all-families-have-grandparents-help-childcare-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehelp%20with%20childcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20share%20expenses.%20We%20also%20intended%20to%20have%20my%20grandma%20move%20into%20one%20of%20our%20extra%20rooms%20so%20we%20could%20help%20support%20her%20in%20her%20golden%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20our%20plans%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%20out%20as%20we%E2%80%99d%20expected.%20My%20grandmother%20died%20before%20the%20house%20was%20even%20finished.%20My%20parents%20only%20lived%20with%20us%20for%20about%20five%20years%20before%20moving%20full%20time%20into%20my%20grandmother's%20old%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20have%20a%20third%20child%2C%20but%20for%20years%20now%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20felt%20like%20we%20have%20too%20much%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20extra%20bedroom%20with%20an%20ensuite%20bathroom%20was%20nice%20while%20my%20parents%20lived%20with%20us%2C%20it%20mostly%20goes%20unused%20now.%20Our%20larger%20home%20comes%20with%20higher%20utility%20bills%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20one%20else%20helping%20us%20to%20pay%20them%20now%20that%20my%20parents%20don't%20live%20here.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20to%20take%20care%20of.%20For%20now%2C%20our%20children%20pitch%20in%20on%20chores%20to%20keep%20things%20tidy%2C%20but%20upkeep%20of%20our%20home%20lies%20on%20our%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20oldest%20is%20now%20a%20year%20away%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-teacher-shares-kids-should-know-before-high-school-ends-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20out%20for%20university%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20know%20our%20house%20will%20only%20seem%20bigger%20and%20emptier%20as%20the%20kids%20head%20off%20to%20college.%3C%2Fp%3