al-announces-7-days-of-savings-offers%2F23c31644-6a28-43d5-b37e-7ede032a6021%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20starts%20on%20July%206.%20The%20dollar%20store's%20discounts%20for%20the%20sale%20are%20more%20limited%20than%20Amazon's%2C%20with%20one%20deal%20per%20day%2C%20such%20as%20a%20discount%20on%20a%20fan%20or%20a%20buy-one%2C%20get-one%20deal%20on%20bratwurst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20and%20Target%2C%20which%20have%20offered%20their%20own%20sales%20around%20Prime%20Day%20in%20years%20past%2C%20are%20also%20getting%20in%20on%20the%20action%20again.%20Walmart's%20sale%2C%20for%20example%2C%20will%20start%20on%20July%208%20and%20run%20for%20six%20days.%20Members%20of%20Walmart%2B%2C%20the%20big%20box%20store's%20paid%20membership%2C%20will%20get%20early%20access%20to%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepartment%20store%20Kohl's%2C%20outdoor%20gear%20retailer%20REI%2C%20and%20home%20improvement%20chain%20Lowe's%20are%20also%20among%20the%20stores%20offering%20Fourth-of-July%20and%20other%20sales%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20Prime%20Day%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20may%20have%20drawn%20inspiration%20from%20its%20rivals%20for%20its%20longer%20Prime%20Day%2C%20Stambor%20said.%20Last%20year%2C%20when%20Prime%20Day%20was%20two%20days%20long%2C%20Walmart's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.walmart.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F06%2F24%2Fwalmart-brings-the-heat-with-its-largest-deals-event-ever%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esale%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20twice%20as%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20can%20see%20that%20those%20events%20have%20resonated%2C%20and%20so%20why%20not%20hop%20in%20the%20pool%20and%20join%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20Stambor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20those%20deals%20could%20be%20welcome%20this%20year%20as%20consumers%20watch%20their%20spending%20closely%20and%20worry%20about%20prices%20going%20up%20due%20to%20tariffs.%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi