roughout%20your%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20her%20story%2C%20not%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20can%20I%20get%20a%20referral%20at%20Google%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20actually%20didn't%20even%20have%20any%20intention%20of%20asking%20her%20for%20this%20internship%20referral%2C%20but%20we%20became%20friends%20and%20she%20let%20me%20into%20her%20life%2C%20which%20is%20what%20her%20day-to-day%20looks%20like%2C%20how%20she%20grows%20in%20the%20role%20that%20she's%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemembering%20that%20professional%20connections%2C%20like%20any%20relationship%2C%20are%20two-way%20streets%2C%20also%20goes%20a%20long%20way%20towards%20helping%20them%20endure%2C%20Doshi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20move%20and%20progress%20in%20our%20life%2C%20the%20way%20in%20which%20I%20think%20about%20it%20is%2C%20we%20are%20collecting%20people%2C%20and%20we%20are%20supporting%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20people%20that%20will%20come%20all%20the%20way%20through%20will%20be%20the%20ones%20that%20you%20have%20formed%20a%20genuine%20bond%20with.%20If%20you%20ask%20someone%20for%20a%20referral%20and%20they%20give%20it%20to%20you%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20that's%20well%20and%20good%2C%20but%20five%20years%20down%20the%20line%2C%2010%20years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20they%20might%20not%20even%20remember%20who%20you%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258a095e9-673b-4705-9c38-966724ff4215%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20can't%20get%20an%20internship%2C%20complete%20a%20project%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20you're%20likely%20to%20be%20taking%20similar%20classes%20as%20your%20competition%2C%20it's%20what%20you%20do%20with%20that%20knowledge%20that%20can%20make%20you%20stand%20out%2C%20Doshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProjects%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Bone%20thing%20that%20I%20will%20say%20again%20and%20again%20and%20again%20for%20any%20student%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Google%20engineer%20partly%20credits%20her%20success%20in%20securing%20an%20internship%20to%20the%20projects%20she%20developed%20in%20her%20downtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20way%20you%20can%20set%20yourself%20apart%20from%201000%20other%20people%2C%20because%20if%20you%20take%20data%20structures%20and%20algorithms%2C%20and%20your%20peers%20take%20data%20structures%20and%20algorithms%2C%20you%20all%20have%20the%20same%20foundational%20knowledge%20that%20you%20are%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20you%20do%20with%20that%20knowledge%2C%20what%20you%20do%20with%20the%20data%20structures%20and%20algorithms%2C%20really%2C%20really%20makes%20a%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20pressure%20to%20specialize%20in%20a%20niche%20skillset%20right%20out%20of%20the%20gate%20to%20impress%20potential%20employers%2C%20either%2C%20Doshi%20said.%20What%20you're%20really%20aiming%20for%20is%20a%20broad%20knowledge%20base%20and%20a%20flexible%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20expect%20you%20to%20come%20in%20with%20tons%20and%20tons%20of%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20actually%20care%20about%20more%20%E2%80%94%20can%20you%20think%20in%20a%20specific%20way%2C%20and%20given%20a%20situation%20changes%2C%20are%20you%20able%20to%20adapt%20to%20that%3F%20More%20than%20doing%20like%20700%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleetcode-coding-test-apple-amazon-google-technical-interview-prep-job-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELeetCode%3C%2Fa%3E%20questions%20and%20getting%20those%20exactly%20right%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20do%20more%20problem%20solving%20in%20adaptive%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f54640d-5203-4a97-ba8c-ae2f84859aa6%5C%22%3EBecoming%20a%20'go-to'%20person%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20and%20when%20you%20finally%20do%20land%20an%20internship%2C%20the%20challenge%20then%20becomes%20securing%20a%20full-t