C%20which%20means%20if%20you're%20stuck%2C%20ask%20the%20right%20person%20for%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20explain%20that%20I%20already%20tried%20to%20do%20X%2C%20Y%2C%20Z%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20work.%20How%20do%20I%20move%20forward%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20an%20internship%20is%2C%20after%20all%2C%20to%20absorb%20as%20much%20knowledge%20as%20possible.%20Try%20to%20avoid%20letting%20your%20fear%20of%20looking%20lost%20halt%20your%20progress%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20this%20kind%20of%20framework%20really%20accelerated%20my%20learnings%2C%20because%20I%20wasn't%20wasting%20hours%20and%20hours%20on%20something%20that%20absolutely%20I%20didn't%20understand%20or%20didn't%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20while%20I%20wasn't%20spending%20those%20hours%2C%20I%20still%20did%20my%20due%20diligence%2C%20which%20is%2C%20do%20my%20research%2C%20look%20through%20the%20code%20base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-engineer-advice-internship-tech-job-offer-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751711101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686701dd85e81483682d6577%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-engineer-advice-internship-tech-job-offer-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aashna%20Doshi%20interned%20at%20Google%20twice%20before%20she%20received%20a%20return%20offer.%20To%20separate%20herself%20from%20the%20pack%2C%20she%20focused%20on%20her%20network%20and%20portfolio.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sperkel%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Perkel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-engineer-advice-internship-tech-job-offer-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Prabhas%20denie