k-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIV%20drips%3C%2Fa%3E).%20As%20the%20personalized%20medicine%20industry%20booms%2C%20Function%20is%20taking%20off.%20The%20company%20says%20its%20membership%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20since%20December%2C%20to%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290d2add0-2e39-4fd9-8e79-7f9136d93ed1%5C%22%3EI%20ended%20up%20overanalyzing%20my%20results%2C%20and%20coming%20to%20some%20pretty%20silly%20conclusions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20very%20first%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20range%26quot%3B%20marker%20that%20was%20mentioned%20in%20my%20Function%20report%20was%20a%20cholesterol%20measurement.%20While%20my%20regular%20LDL%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bbad%26quot%3B%20cholesterol%20number%20%E2%80%94%20the%20one%20you'd%20get%20measured%20in%20a%20doctor's%20office%20%E2%80%94%20looked%20fine%2C%20Function%20also%20measured%20the%20size%20of%20my%20LDL%20cholesterol%20particles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20I%20had%20slightly%20elevated%20numbers%20of%20small%20and%20medium%20sized%20LDL%20cholesterol%20particles%2C%20which%20are%20more%20dangerous%20than%20larger%20LDL%20particles.%20This%20%26quot%3Bcould%20indicate%20an%20increased%20risk%20for%20cardiovascular%20disease%20despite%20normal%20LDL%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20results%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20vital%20to%20address%20the%20out-of-range%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20surprise.%20I%20had%20always%20been%20told%20I%20have%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20cholesterol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20imagining%20all%20those%20tiny%2C%20sticky%20cholesterol%20particles%20racing%20towards%20my%20aging%20heart.%20Knowing%20how%20important%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheart-healthy-habits-reverse-biological-age-study-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20health%20is%20for%20healthy%20aging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20heart%20disease%20is%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20started%20to%20worry.%20Should%20I%20quit%20my%20beloved%20mayonnaise%3F%20Maybe%20I%20should%20at%20least%20cut%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20initial%20shock%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20independent%20cardiologists%20and%20longevity%20doctors%20for%20this%20story.%20I%20also%20spoke%20directly%20to%20Hyman%20about%20my%20results.%20All%20of%20those%20physicians%20refocused%20my%20attention%2C%20helping%20me%20interpret%20the%20results%2C%20and%20zoom%20in%20on%20the%20more%20meaningful%20ways%20to%20adjust%20my%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrankly%2C%20they%20reminded%20me%20why%20this%20kind%20of%20testing%20isn't%20widely%20recommended%2C%20and%20why%20we%20go%20to%20the%20doctor%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e98fa65b-9a2a-42c9-98de-72b2656c9dd1%5C%22%3EWithout%20help%20from%20doctors%2C%20I%20was%20stressing%20about%20the%20wrong%20things%20in%20my%20labs%20and%20on%20my%20plate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225142%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hand%20with%20lots%20of%20different%20supplements%20in%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672e566d88cea3ba1c1f3fe5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223449%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFunction%20recommended%20five%20supplements%20for%20me%3A%20vitamin%20D%2C%20omega-3%2C%20CoQ10%2C%20berberine%2C%20and%20fiber.%3Cp%3EStrauss%2FCurtis%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20for%20me%2C%20a%20seasoned%20health%20journalist%20who%20isn't%20generally%20freaked%20out%20by%20medical%20test%20results%2C%20this%20felt%20like%20a%20lot%20to%20take%20in.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20supposedly%20off-balance%20cholesterol%20numbers%2C%20there%20was%20also%20low%20vitamin%20D%2C%20and%20a%20few%20other%20items%20that%20could%20impact%20everything%20from%20my%20immunity%20to%20metabolism%20and%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20a%20doctor's%20advice%2C%20I%20found%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20noise%20of%20all%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20you%20showed%20any%20cardiologist%20or%20lipidologist%20your%20panel%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20worrying%20about%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Ken%20Feingold%2C%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20who%20is%20an%20expert%20on%20lipids%20and%20lipoprotein%20metabolism%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cholesterol%20numbers%20that%20really%20matter%20were%20fine%2C%20including%20the%20basics%20(total%20cholesterol%2C%20LDL%2C%20HDL)%20but%20also%20some%20of%20the%20more%20niche%20measurements%20that%20doctors%20are%20now%20factoring%20into%20clinical%20decision-making%2C%20like%20lipoprotein%20A%20and%20apolipoprotein%20B%20(APOB)%2C%20Feingold%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20would%20be%20very%20unfair%20to%20expect%20a%20consumer%2C%20the%20person%20that%20had%20the%20lab%20work%20done%20to%20try%20and%20figure%20it%20out%20on%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20David%20Sabgir%2C%20a%20cardiologist%20in%20Ohio%20who%20is%20also%20not%20involved%20with%20Function%20Health%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20Function%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20consumers%20make%20simple%20nutrition%20tweaks%20they%20hadn't%20thought%20to%20make%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20adding%20fatty%20fish%20for%20omega-3%2C%20vitamin%20D%2C%20or%20fiber%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B80%25%20of%20people's%20health%20issues%20will%20never%20need%20a%20doctor%2C%26quot%3B%20Hyman%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20really%20lifestyle-driven%20and%20they%20can%20be%20modified%20through%20modifying%20your%20diet%20and%20your%20lifestyle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20a%20consumer%2C%20I%20found%20the%20barrage%20of%20information%20confusing%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20to%20feel%20in%20control%20of%20good%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20while%20Function%20gave%20me%20diet%20and%20supplement%20recommendations%20(vitamin%20D%2C%20fiber%2C%20berberine%2C%20omega-3%2C%20and%20coQ10%2C%20along%20with%20more%20fish%20and%20eggs)%2C%20it%20buried%20the%20most%20important%20piece%20of%20nutrition%20advice%20that%20every%20doctor%20I%20spoke%20to%20was%20quickly%20able%20to%20point%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d701cd4-7837-4216-87ac-d73dbbadc187%5C%22%3EDoctors%20told%20me%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20white%20bread%20and%20enjoy%20avocados%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22avocado%20toast%20on%20a%20plate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686595c6f748d8c055f4de2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDoctors%20recommended%20replacing%20white%20bread%20with%20whole%20grains%2C%20and%20enjoying%20healthy%20fats%20like%20avocados.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20interview%20with%20Hyman%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20not%20standard%20procedure%20for%20Function%20patients%20%E2%80%94%20he%20told%20me%20I%20could%20improve%20my%20particle%20numbers%20by%20cutting%20down%20on%2C%20or%20ideally%20eliminating%2C%20refined%20starches%20and%20sugars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20advice%20that%20was%20not%20highlighted%20in%20my%20Function%20dashboard%2C%20but%20other%20doctors%20wholeheartedly%20agreed.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiora%20longevity%20clinic%20director%20Dr.%20Gregory%20Pippert%20uses%20advanced%20blood%20testing%20that's%20similar%20to%20Function's%2C%20often%20catering%20to%20patients%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20optimize%20their%20health%20and%20gains%20in%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%20so%20much%20green%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20my%20cholesterol%20panel.%20%26quot%3BThen%20I%20see%20particle%20numbers%20that%20are%20not%20massively%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Pippert%2C%20the%20headline%20was%20simple%3A%20just%20skip%20the%20refined%20grains%20more%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20I%20really%2C%20really%20need%20the%20big%20extra%20thick%20slice%20of%20white%20bread%3F%20Maybe%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Pippert%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20making%20the%20good%20choices%20more%20than%20the%20bad%20choices%2C%20but%20not%20obsessing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20more%20granular%20data%20may%20help%20some%20patients%20take%20general%20pieces%20of%20health%20advice%20%E2%80%94%20to%20hit%20the%20gym%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20incorporate%20more%20strength%20training%2C%20or%20adhere%20to%20heart%20healthy%20diets%2C%20like%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet%2C%20more%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20anxiety%20associated%20with%20the%20results%20may%20trigger%20more%20compliance%20with%20lifestyle%20modification%2C%26quot%3B%20Sabgir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20can%20we%20be%20sure%20we'll%20pick%20out%20the%20right%20tweaks%20on%20our%20own%3F%20If%20I'm%20skipping%20mayo%20but%20not%20switching%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhole-grain-bigger-meals-provide-more-energy-dietitian-advice-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhole%20grains%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20cutting%20back%20on%20sugar%2C%20I'm%20probably%20not%20going%20to%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20my%20test%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20why%20people%20are%20offering%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Feingold%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20way%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20because%20sure%2C%20they're%20charging%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20money%20for%20this%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20really%20need%20it%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20who%20you're%20going%20to%20treat%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffunction-health-500-dollar-blood-test-i-tried-it-2025-7%5C%2