e%20he%20hopes%20his%20financial%20situation%20and%20mental%20well-being%20will%20improve.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20from%20America%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20achieve%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-dream-shrinking-smaller-homes-fewer-kids-vacation-time-commutes-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmerican%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20I%20stayed%20in%20the%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20graduated%20from%20college%20on%20the%20heels%20of%202008's%20Great%20Recession.%20It%20seemed%20like%20nobody%20was%20hiring.%20I%20built%20a%20career%20writing%20for%20travel%20magazines%20and%20news%20outlets%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20student%20loan%20payments%20that%20started%20at%20around%20%24900%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20COVID%20hit%2C%20I%20lost%20clients%2C%20and%20my%20financial%20situation%20became%20dire.%20Loans%20and%20rent%20gobbled%20up%20nearly%20%242%2C000%20a%20month%20before%20car%20payments.%20I%20moved%20in%20with%20my%20sister%20and%20then%20tried%20living%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lonelyplanet.com%2Farticles%2Fcampervan-road-trip-in-pandemic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edirt-cheap%20trailer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20make%20up%20for%20the%20income%20I%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20my%20life%20in%20the%20US%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-nyc-to-argentina-adults-more-patient-with-kids-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20Argentina%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20two%20dogs.%20I%20hoped%20the%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20abroad%20would%20help%20me%20slash%20expenses%20and%20reduce%20my%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20time%2C%20everything%20clicked.%20I%20saved%20money%20and%20began%20paying%20down%20debts%2C%20but%20with%20the%20financial%20success%20came%20a%20darker%20side%20to%20living%20abroad.%20I%20struggled%20to%20connect%20with%20locals%2C%20and%20my%20isolation%