%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67688727%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevalued%20the%20peso%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fsep%2F27%2Fpoverty-rate-argentina-milei%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPoverty%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20reached%20their%20highest%20level%20in%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20was%20felt%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20my%20own%20rent%20and%20utility%20costs%20living%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%20increased%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20been%20struggling%20with%20a%20growing%20sense%20of%20loneliness%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-new-orleans-to-buenos-aires-after-break-up-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20to%20Argentina%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20my%20best%20efforts%2C%20I%20hadn't%20made%20close%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20began%20experiencing%20bouts%20of%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stuck%20with%20it%20because%20of%20the%20progress%20I'd%20made%20with%20paying%20down%20my%20debt%2C%20but%20the%20economic%20changes%20were%20making%20loan%20repayments%20more%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20of%20my%20two%20dogs%20died.%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20make%20a%20change%20before%20my%20emotional%20state%20declined%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22953a196a-1031-44b3-b155-dd04874c0153%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20same%20parameters%20as%20before%2C%20I%20set%20out%20looking%20for%20an%20affordable%20country%20to%20move%20to%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20enjoys%20staying%20on%20top%20of%20travel%20trends%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-i-loved-that-should-be-more-popular-frequent-traveler-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlbania%3C%2Fa%3E%20piqued%20my%20interest.%20The%20coastal%20photographs%20looked%20so%20nice%20that%20I%20thought%20they%20were%20AI-generated.%20I%20noticed%20US%20passport%20holders%20could%20enter%20for%20a%20full%2012%20months%20as%20tourists%20without%20applying%20for%20a%20residency%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202025%2C%20I%20moved%20into%20a%20furnished%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Tirana%2C%20Albania's%20capital%20city%2C%20for%20roughly%20%24600.%20With%20utilities%2C%20the%20first%20month%20cost%20%24650.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlbania%20still%20remains%20somewhat%20of%20a%20new%20expat%20destination.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20the%20brand%20appeal%20of%20Spain%20or%20Italy%2C%20but%20locals%20I've%20asked%20have%20noticed%20a%20big%20increase%20in%20outsiders%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlbania's%20economy%20seems%20stable%2C%20which%20should%20provide%20me%20with%20predictable%20monthly%20expenses.%20I'd%20say%20most%20things%20are%20cheaper%20here%20than%20in%20Argentina.%20A%20cup%20of%20coffee%20costs%20me%20just%20%240.59%20per%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20take%20some%20time%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20much%20spare%20cash%20I'll%20have%20to%20pay%20off%20debt%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%2C%20since%20there%20are%20resettling%20costs%20involved%20in%20a%20move%2C%20like%20buying%20new%20dishes%20and%20a%20vacuum%20cleaner%20for%20the%20ever-shedding%20dog.%20I'll%20be%20happy%20if%20my%20expenses%20start%20to%20look%20remotely%20close%20to%20what%20my%20early%20Argentina%20days%20were%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22360ec6b2-8c42-443e-9b69-9dc6f41f063d%5C%22%3EI've%20learned%20you%20can't%20be%20prepared%20for%20everything%20when%20you%20move%20abroad%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Argentina%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20prepared.%20I'd%20researched%20the%20country%20and%20its%20occasionally%20volatile%20economy%2C%20which%20was%20financially%20beneficial%20to%20non-peso%20earners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-tips-moving-abroad-with-kids-living-overseas-family-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20involves%20handing%20over%20power.%20Hopping%20on%20a%20plane%20and%20settling%20somewhere%20new%20is%20invigorating%2C%20but%20also%20terrifying.%20You%20can't%20account%20for%20the%20unknowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20Argentina%20for%20financial%20gain%2C%20but%20had%20no%20idea%20I'd%20struggle%20making%20friends%2C%20or%20that%20the%20extended%20isolation%20would%20lead%20to%20depression.%20I%20still%20wouldn't%20change%20anything%20about%20this%20difficult%20patch%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20part%20of%20my%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20digital%20nomad%20experience%20is%20fluid%2C%20and%20your%20experiences%20aren't%20always%20positive.%20This%20fluidity%20has%20washed%20me%20into%20Albania.%20The%20country's%20friendly%20nature%20makes%20me%20hopeful%20my%20life%20will%20improve%20not%20only%20financially%20but%20mentally%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20relocating%20for%20financial%20reasons%3F%20Contact%20the%20editor%2C%20Charissa%20Cheong%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Accheong%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eccheong%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-argentina-us-albania-student-loans-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751707861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866505e3d5881a51c1c9dce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-argentina-us-albania-student-loans-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Greyson%20Ferguson%20left%20the%20US%20for%20Buenos%20Aires%20in%202022.%20But%20when%20living%20in%20Argentina%20grew%20more%20costly%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Albania%20in%20search%20of%20a%20cheaper%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Greyson%20Ferguson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canoni