y%20right%20now%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-ai-replace-take-over-create-jobs-debate-tech-leaders-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20impact%20of%20AI%20on%20people's%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20can%20also%20take%20your%20cue%20from%20what%20others%20in%20your%20network%20are%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20building%20your%20network%2C%20send%20a%20personalized%20note%20with%20every%20connection%20request%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20noise%2C%20explain%20why%20you're%20reaching%20out%2C%20and%20refresh%20someone's%20memory%20of%20where%20you%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20you%20want%20the%20parts%20of%20your%20profile%20to%20work%20together%20to%20make%20people%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20like%20they%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Granger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20your%20profile%20to%20be%20able%20to%20start%20a%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-dos-and-donts-of-linkedin-expert-advice%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751707621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686566b83d5881a51c1c8e45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-dos-and-donts-of-linkedin-expert-advice%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Experts%20shared%20their%20tips%20on%20optimizing%20your%20LinkedIn%20profile%20and%20building%20your%20professional%20brand%20on%20the%20site%20to%20aid%20your%20job%20search.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sjackson%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Jackson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-dos-and-donts-of-linkedin-expert-advice%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20LinkedIn%20cold-outreach%20template%20helped%20job%20seekers%20land%20roles%