NBA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20AEW%20founder%20and%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faew-mjf-steiner-math-his-idea-tony-khan-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETony%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%20fired%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20picking%20up%20traction%20in%20these%20key%20demos%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20that%20among%2018-%20to%2024-year-olds%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20the%20growth%20is%20on%20streaming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20ratings%20are%20trending%20higher%2C%20AEW%20is%20still%20clawing%20its%20way%20back%20out%20of%20a%20slump.%20Viewership%20for%20%26quot%3BCollision%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDynamite%26quot%3B%20was%20down%209%25%20and%2012%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20year%20over%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAEW%20has%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20battle%20with%20the%20category's%20behemoth%2C%20WWE%2C%20which%20previously%20poached%20two%20of%20its%20biggest%20stars%3A%20Cody%20Rhodes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faew-owner-tony-khan-interview-firing-cm-punk-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECM%20Punk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20a%20lifelong%20wrestling%20fan%2C%20spoke%20with%20BI%20about%20how%20streaming%20has%20jump-started%20AEW's%20growth%20and%20why%20he's%20not%20sweating%20the%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarner-bros-discovery-split-two-companies-streaming-studios-global-networks-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espinoff%20at%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20his%20most%20valuable%20business%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a0eba58-b79c-4bae-80ba-7c629f38f403%5C%22%3EAEW%20everywhere%2C%20all%20at%20once%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20cutthroat%2C%20crowded%20media%20landscape%2C%20Khan's%20game%20plan%20is%20for%20AEW%20to%20be%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94