ty%2C%20but%20also%20consume%20highlights%20on%20digital%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20found%20a%20great%20balance%20in%20that%2C%20and%20also%20offering%20access%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20great%20classic%20matches%20in%20the%20AEW%20library%20to%20the%20fans%20has%20helped%20us%20drive%20a%20lot%20of%20viewership%2C%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAEW%20must%20thread%20the%20needle%20between%20maximizing%20reach%20and%20ensuring%20that%20live%20matches%20and%20pay-per-view%20events%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Khan%20put%20it.%20That%20means%20giving%20enough%20to%20lure%20casual%20fans%20and%20newcomers%20to%20TBS%2C%20TNT%2C%20and%20HBO%20Max%2C%20without%20giving%20so%20much%20that%20they%20don't%20watch%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAEW%20streams%20pre-%20and%20post-shows%20live%20on%20YouTube%20for%20big%20matches.%20But%20some%20of%20AEW's%20rivals%20are%20going%20a%20step%20further%20by%20experimenting%20with%20livestreaming%20marquee%20events%20on%20YouTube%2C%20for%20free.%20WWE%20streamed%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Flive%2Fv4M2vvIWahQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWorlds%20Collide%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20live%20on%20the%20platform%20in%20early%20June%2C%20and%20the%20NFL%20is%20hosting%20a%20regular-season%20game%20live%20on%20YouTube%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Khan%20isn't%20following%20suit.%20The%20AEW%20CEO%20said%20he's%20firmly%20committed%20to%20TBS%2C%20TNT%2C%20and%20HBO%20Max%2C%20no%20matter%20what's%20happening%20at%20their%20parent%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc43978a-8c22-4d4c-aea4-0b7cd17bfcde%5C%22%3ENot%20splitting%20hairs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWBD%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwbd-spinoff-david-zaslav-wall-street-studios-streaming-tv-networks-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-awaited%20spinoff%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20that%20will%20pull%20HBO%20Max%20away%20from%20TBS%20and%20TNT.%20Khan%20said%20the%20split%20shouldn't%20affect%20AEW%2C%20which%20reached%20a%20media%20deal%20with%20WBD%20last%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20great%20partnership%20with%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20AEW%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20well%20entrenched%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20forthcoming%20Streaming%20%26amp%3B%20Studios%20and%20Global%20Networks%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD's%20media%20rights%20deal%20with%20AEW%20is%20unaffected%20by%20the%20split%2C%20so%20HBO%20Max%20will%20continue%20to%20stream%20matches%20that%20air%20live%20on%20TBS%20and%20TNT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20a%20top%20media%20analyst%20thinks%20sports%20leagues%20like%20AEW%20should%20brainstorm%20alternatives%20for%20their%20next%20deals%20in%20light%20of%20the%20spinoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20broadcast%20network%20or%20a%20streaming%20platform%20(we%20are%20not%20counting%20Discovery%2B)%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20imagine%20sports%20leagues%20being%20excited%20to%20work%20with%20GLN%20%5BGlobal%20Linear%20Networks%5D%20going%20forward%2C%20unless%20they%20have%20no%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Lightshed's%20Rich%20Greenfield%20wrote%20in%20a%20mid-June%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAEW%20has%20seen%20firsthand%20how%20HBO%20Max%20can%20effectively%20complement%20TBS%20and%20TNT.%20Once%20they%20belong%20to%20separate%20companies%2C%20that%20symbiosis%20could%20disappear.%20And%20while%20AEW%20could%20theoretically%20re-up%20with%20TNT%20Sports%20and%20find%20a%20separate%20streaming%20deal%2C%20Greenfield%20questioned%20that%20logic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGLN%20could%20license%20its%20sports%20streaming%20rights%20to%20third-parties%20(assuming%20contracts%20allow%20it)%26quot%3B%20Greenfield%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20why%20would%20a%20sports%20rights%20holder%20not%20just%20choose%20a%20vertically-integrated%20platform%20to%20begin%20with%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20analysts%20are%20less%20bearish%2C%20including%20Robert%20Fishman%20of%20MoffettNathanson.%20He%20wrote%20last%20month%20that%20%26quot%3Bsports%20remains%20a%20key%20pillar%20to%20support%20affiliate%20fee%20stability%20in%20the%20years%20ahead%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Global%20Networks%20business%20that%20will%20house%20TBS%20and%20TNT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20wondering%20what%20the%20future%20holds%20for%20WBD's%20assets%2C%20Khan%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20present.%20The%20100th%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BCollision%26quot%3B%20airs%20Saturday%20night%2C%20and%20viewers%20can%20tune%20in%20on%20TNT%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Max.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faew-tony-khan-interview-streaming-hbo-max-tnt-tbs-youtube-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751707202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686576f0f748d8c055f4d890%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faew-tony-khan-interview-streaming-hbo-max-tnt-tbs-youtube-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AEW%20CEO%20Tony%20Khan%20said%20cable%20ratings%20have%20risen%20while%20simulcasting%20on%20HBO%20Max.%20He%20shared%20his%20YouTube%20strategy%2C%20and%20why%20he's%20not%20sweating%20WBD's%20split.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faew-tony-khan-interview-streaming-hbo-max-tnt-tbs-youtube-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forget%20fundamentals.%204%20everyday%20investors%20have%20made%20winning%20stock%20picks%20with%20a%20much%20simpler%20strategy.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20graph%20with%20a%20car%2C%20computer%20and%20clothes%20in%20the%20middle%20with%20a%20blue%20stock%20ar