Echortens%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20sacred%20juniper%20stands%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Namgail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoosing%20to%20stay%20in%20one%20of%20these%20homestays%20generates%20funds%20for%20communities%20that%20they%20use%20to%20protect%20their%20mountain%20environment.%20The%20villagers%20also%20host%20guests%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20done%20so%20that%20no%20single%20family%20can%20monopolise%20the%20tourists.%20Because%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20create%20disharmony%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20livestock%20and%20landscapes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservancy%20also%20supports%20the%20construction%20of%20predator-proof%20livestock%20enclosures%20using%20low-cost%20and%20locally%20sourced%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CVillagers%20provide%20the%20labour%20while%20SLC-IT%20provides%20wire%20mesh%2C%20doorframes%2C%20beams%2C%20and%20wooden%20poles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Namgail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance.%20It%20preys%20on%20herbivores%20such%20as%20the%20Himalayan%20blue%20sheep%20and%20Asiatic%20ibex%2C%20keeping%20their%20populations%20in%20check%20and%20preventing%20overgrazing.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20herbivores%20feed%20on%20alpine%20pastures%20that%20grow%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F321695%2Faamir-khanyari-turned-ancestral-land-into-traditional-kashmir-homestay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslopes%20of%20the%20mountain%20ranges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20controlling%20the%20population%20of%20these%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20the%20snow%20leopard%20gives%20the%20grasses%20and%20plants%20a%20chance%20to%20regenerate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Namgail%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wild%20Images%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-462677%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wild%20Images%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20ecological%20balance%20has%20knock-on%20effects.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%20we%20are%20receiving%20more%20rain%20and%20less%20snow.%20As%20the%20rainwater%20flows%20down%20the%20slopes%2C%20the%20loose%20soil%20also%20goes%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20soil%20is%20loosened%20by%20the%20grazing%20activity%20of%20goats.%20The%20presence%20of%20the%20